{% comment %}
Dependencies: 
  wishlist-page.css


Need to do js.
Js class 
  - for open the dropdowns add "open" class in the parent of dropdown
  - For the popup open Add the "popup-show overflow-hidden" class in the body
    Also i added the hidden class for hide the display so add/remove that class according to data display

{% endcomment %}
 


{{ 'wishlist-page.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
{{ 'component-pagination.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

